Package: scvis
Type: Package
Title: Dimensionality reduction of single cell data
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(person("Pascale", "Walters", email = "pwalters@bccrc.ca", role = c("aut", "cre")), person("Jiarui", "Ding",  role = "aut"))
URL: https://github.com/pascalewalters/scvis
BugReports: https://github.com/pascalewalters/scvis/issues
Description: A package to perform dimensional reduction for single cell data that is robust to the number of cells. It uses a probablistic parametric mapping function to add new data points to the model.
License: Apache License (>= 2.0)
LazyData: true
Imports:
    reticulate,
    SingleCellExperiment,
    yaml
SystemRequirements:
    python3,
    tensorflow
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
